{"id":410,"date":"2018-11-10T04:37:28","date_gmt":"2018-11-09T21:37:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=410"},"modified":"2018-12-25T15:44:49","modified_gmt":"2018-12-25T08:44:49","slug":"giai-phap-thiet-ke-mau-nha-1-tang-3-phong-ngu-chi-voi-800-trieu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/giai-phap-thiet-ke-mau-nha-1-tang-3-phong-ngu-chi-voi-800-trieu","title":{"rendered":"&#8220;GI\u1ea2I PH\u00c1P THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe&#8221; M\u1eabu nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi 800 tri\u1ec7u"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"project--description formatted-text blockquote-lang-vn !margin-l-none-xs\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 cao t\u1ea7ng th\u00ec l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn x\u00e2y nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n khi qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec7n nghi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/giai-phap-thiet-ke-mau-nha-1-tang-3-phong-ngu-chi-voi-800-trieu\"><em><strong>m\u1eabu nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi 800 tri\u1ec7u<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span>.\u00a0Ch\u0103\u0301c ch\u0103\u0301n ba\u0323n se\u0303 ha\u0300i lo\u0300ng khi l\u01b0\u0323a cho\u0323n gia\u0309i pha\u0301p thi\u00ea\u0301t k\u00ea\u0301 x\u00e2y d\u01b0\u0323ng na\u0300y cho gia\u00a0\u0111i\u0300nh mi\u0300nh.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8220;GI\u1ea2I PH\u00c1P THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe&#8221; M\u1eabu nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi 800 tri\u1ec7u<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 t\u1ed5ng quan ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac:<\/strong> Nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng (nh\u00e0 c\u1ea5p 4).<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; C\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>1 pho\u0300ng kha\u0301ch<\/li>\n<li>3 pho\u0300ng ngu\u0309<\/li>\n<li>1 pho\u0300ng b\u00ea\u0301p + pho\u0300ng \u0103n<\/li>\n<li>2 nha\u0300 v\u00ea\u0323 sinh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch:<\/strong> 8.7m x 28m<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; T\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<\/strong> 800 tri\u1ec7u<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khu \u0111\u1ea5t c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u01a1n <strong>240 m2 (8.7m x 28m)<\/strong>. V\u00ec th\u1ebf gia ch\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng c\u00f3 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, m\u1ed9t Gara \u0111\u1ec3 xe v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 800 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u00e2y xanh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-411 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-m\u1eb7t-b\u1eb1ng-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"680\" height=\"357\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nha\u0300\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c thi\u00ea\u0301t k\u00ea\u0301 v\u01a1\u0301i nhi\u00ea\u0300u khoa\u0309ng s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1\u0300n xanh ma\u0301t. L\u00f4\u0301i thi\u00ea\u0301t k\u00ea\u0301 th\u00f4ng minh, ng\u00f4i nha\u0300 1 t\u00e2\u0300ng v\u01a1\u0301i 3 pho\u0300ng ngu\u0309 tr\u00f4ng r\u00e2\u0301t th\u00f4ng thoa\u0301ng. Ca\u0301c pho\u0300ng \u0111\u00ea\u0300u co\u0301 c\u01b0\u0309a s\u00f4\u0309 n\u00ean lu\u00f4n co\u0301 a\u0301nh sa\u0301ng t\u01b0\u0323 nhi\u00ean va\u0300 kh\u00f4ng khi\u0301 l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng trong pho\u0300ng.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nhu c\u1ea7u mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/thiet-ke-nha-pho-da-nang\">C\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng<\/a><\/span> uy t\u00edn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch sang tr\u1ecdng, tinh t\u1ebf<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 nh\u01b0ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi gam m\u00e0u nh\u00e3 nh\u1eb7n, \u0111\u1ea7y sang tr\u1ecdng. C\u1eeda k\u00ednh l\u1edbn trong su\u1ed1t gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian b\u00ean trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-412 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 b\u00e0n g\u1ed7 v\u00e0 Sofa sang tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi gam n\u00e2u nhu, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng chanh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc g\u1ed1i trang tr\u00ed. Chi\u1ebfc th\u1ea3m l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7t d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ed9 b\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5m c\u00fang, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sum v\u1ea7y.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-413 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec7n nghi<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n, b\u1ed3n r\u1eeda b\u00e1t, m\u00e1y h\u00fat m\u00f9i, l\u00f2 vi s\u00f3ng&#8230; t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u00eam tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-414 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. T\u1eeb b\u00e0n, gh\u1ebf, b\u1ebfp, \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u00f2a. T\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c b\u1ebfp, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn ra c\u00e2y xanh t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1ed1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m \u0111i s\u1ef1 ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 c\u0103n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-415 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. Khu v\u1ef1c th\u1edd c\u00fang trang nghi\u00eam, thanh t\u1ecbnh<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t ri\u00eang d\u00e0nh cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1edd c\u00fang gia ti\u00ean. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u00e0n th\u1edd b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thanh l\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 t\u0129nh l\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n nghi\u00eam. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 b\u00e0n gh\u1ebf d\u00e0i, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch, u\u1ed1ng tr\u00e0 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-416 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. Ph\u00f2ng v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh<\/strong> l\u00e0 n\u01a1i hay \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, n\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-417 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"427\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>5. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">&#8211; Pho\u0300ng ngu\u0309 master l\u01a1\u0301n co\u0301\u00a0WC ri\u00eang:<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\"> Kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u00e2\u0300m l\u0103\u0301ng, mang la\u0323i ca\u0309m gia\u0301c th\u01b0 tha\u0301i khi thi\u00ea\u0301t k\u00ea\u0301 sa\u0300n, gi\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng, k\u00ea\u0323 b\u0103\u0300ng g\u00f4\u0303 n\u00e2u. Phi\u0301a tr\u00ean\u00a0\u0111\u00e2\u0300u gi\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng la\u0300 b\u01b0\u0301c tranh la\u0300m c\u0103n pho\u0300ng th\u00eam sinh\u00a0\u0111\u00f4\u0323ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-418 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eeda s\u1ed5 b\u1eb1ng k\u00ednh l\u1edbn t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ed9ng th\u00eam ra. T\u1eeb trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn ra kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3i c\u1ecf xanh m\u01b0\u1edbt.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-419 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a con trai v\u00e0 con g\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i vui, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f4\u0303i c\u0103n pho\u0300ng\u00a0\u0111\u00ea\u0300u co\u0301 n\u00f4\u0323i th\u00e2\u0301t\u00a0\u0111\u00e2\u0300y\u00a0\u0111u\u0309 nh\u01b0: gi\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng, ba\u0300n ho\u0323c, tu\u0309 qu\u00e2\u0300n\u00a0a\u0301o,\u2026\u00a0\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian qua hai chi\u1ebfc c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u00f3 m\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c tranh ng\u00f4\u0323\u00a0ngh\u0129nh va\u0300 nh\u01b0\u0303ng\u00a0\u0111\u00f4\u0300 trang tri\u0301\u00a0\u0111a\u0301ng y\u00eau.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-420 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"447\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-421 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tham kh\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_422\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-422\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-422 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"386\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-422\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(M\u1eabu nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng m\u00e1i tha\u0301i 3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u1ecf)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_423\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-423\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-423 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-423\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 1 t\u1ea7ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_424\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-424\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-424 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-424\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(C\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi g\u1ea1ch tr\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m xuy\u1ebft sang tr\u1ecdng)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_425\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-425\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-425 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GI\u1ea2I-PH\u00c1P-THI\u1ebeT-K\u1ebe-M\u1eabu-nh\u00e0-1-t\u1ea7ng-3-ph\u00f2ng-ng\u1ee7-ch\u1ec9-v\u1edbi-800-tri\u1ec7u14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" hei